<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.css"
     integrity="sha512-5A8nwdMOWrSz20fDsjczgUidUBR8liPYU+WymTZP1lmY9G6Oc7HlZv156XqnsgNUzTyMefFTcsFH/tnJE/+xBg==" 
     crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">    
    <title>Registration Success</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">

    <style>
       #container{
    
   display:flex;
   flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
      margin: auto;
      column-gap: 5em;
      

 }
 #card{
     border-radius: 10px;
     width: 300px;
     line-height: 30px;
     box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07) 0px 1px 2px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07) 0px 2px 4px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07) 0px 4px 8px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07) 0px 8px 16px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07) 0px 16px 32px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07) 0px 32px 64px;
 }
 p{
     color:black;
     display: block;
     text-align: center;

 }

@media screen and (max-width:676px) {
  #container
  {
    row-gap: 3em;
  }
}


.btn {
 background: #d97b34;
 background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #d97b34, #b82f2b);
 background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #d97b34, #b82f2b);
 background-image: -ms-linear-gradient(top, #d97b34, #b82f2b);
 background-image: -o-linear-gradient(top, #d97b34, #b82f2b);
 background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #d97b34, #b82f2b);
 -webkit-border-radius: 26;
 -moz-border-radius: 26;
 border-radius: 26px;
 font-family: Georgia;
 color: #ffffff;
 font-size: 18px;
 padding: 9px 20px 10px 20px;
 text-decoration: none;
}

.btn:hover {
 background: #3cb0fd;
 background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #3cb0fd, #3498db);
 background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #3cb0fd, #3498db);
 background-image: -ms-linear-gradient(top, #3cb0fd, #3498db);
 background-image: -o-linear-gradient(top, #3cb0fd, #3498db);
 background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #3cb0fd, #3498db);
 text-decoration: none;
}


#Paycontainer
      {
      width: 300px;
      height: 450px;
      }
      img{
       width: 300px;
      height: 450px;

      }
      .note{
        text-align: center;
       margin-top: 50px;
       margin-bottom: 50px;
       height: 20%;
       width: 90%;
       color:#b82f2b;
      }
      .cards{
       box-shadow: rgba(237, 233, 233, 0.07) 0px 1px 2px, rgba(245, 242, 242, 0.07) 0px 2px 4px, rgba(249, 249, 249, 0.07) 0px 4px 8px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07) 0px 8px 16px, rgba(239, 236, 236, 0.07) 0px 16px 32px, rgba(247, 246, 246, 0.07) 0px 32px 64px;
       
      }

   

    </style>
  </head>
  
  <body>

    <main>
     
      <div class="card">
       
        <p style="font-size: 25px;">Thank you for registering for the<b> Ekarikthin'23</b></p>
        
       
      </div>
      <div class="note"><div class="cards">
       <p> After the Successful payment send the screenshot to the  <i class="fa fa-whatsapp" aria-hidden="true"></i> <b>9704501824</b> To receive confirmation of your payment. <b>OR</b> You can complete your payment at the Venue.</p>
        
        Produce the following DETAILS at helpdesk to receive your receipt. Without a receipt, you will not be able to participate in the event.
    </div></div>
      
     <div id="container">
        <div id="card" >
         <p style="font-weight: bold; font-size: medium;">Registration Details :</p>
         
            <p >NAME : <%=user.name%></p>
            <p>EVENT : <%=user.event%></p>
            <p style="color:red">TOKEN ID : <%=user.tokenId%></p>
            <p>EMAIL : <%=user.email%></p>
            <p>CATEGORY : <%=user.category%></p>
            <p>COST : <%=user.cost%></p>
            <p>PAYMENT MODE : <%=user.paymentMode%></p>
        </div>
      
        <div id='Paycontainer'>
            <img src="/pay.jpeg">
     </div>
     
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <button class="btn" style="margin: 20px;" onclick = "window.location.href ='/'">Click to Redirect to Home Page</button></div>
    </div>
       </main>
    </main>

  </body>
</html>

